[1] Zeisel, A. et al. - Cell types in the mouse cortex and hippocampus revealed by single-cell RNA-seq. Science 347, 1138\'961142 (2015); \
dataset from https://hemberg-lab.github.io/scRNA.seq.datasets/mouse/brain/#zeisel\
